inspirations.contestRules:
1.Participation.
1.1 Prize for the monthly Rejuvenation Challenge is shown on its page and depends on the number of registered users.
1.2 You have to be registered in FaceLift Naturally app to take part of the contest.
1.3 Upload 6 pictures Before when you start your rejuvenation course. Then upload 6 pictures After when you finished each Study or Practice course. You can upload as many sets of pictures After as you wish but only the latest uploaded will be in your challenge collage.
1.4 Let others see your pictures in the Rules of the Challenge. Your results will be available to the Jury of the Challenge. The Jury will choose maximum 10 most competitive collages for the monthly challenge.
1.5 You can take part in contest as many times as you wish while your subscription is active. Every time your set of pictures After have to be renewed.
2. Voting
2.1 Challenge collages are posted for the Voting every month.
2.2 Anyone can vote for the result with ¬´like¬ª tapped under the winners collage.
2.2.1 ¬´Like¬ª of the registered user with purchased course counts as 10 votes.
2.2.2 ¬´Like¬ª of register user without purchase counts as 5 votes.
2.2.3 ¬´Like¬ª of non registered user counts as 1 vote.
2.3 You can ¬´like¬ª as many participants results as you wish. Only 1 ¬´like¬ª for each participant will be counted.
2.4 Voting ends on last day of the current month.
2.5 Participant with biggest number of votes wins the Challenge.
3 Prize.
3.1 We pay the prize to the winner during the next month from Challenge ends.
3.2 Winner must be registered in FaceLift. We contact the winner via email to receive payments details.
3.3 It is winner responsibility to pay taxes on the prize money if they are applicable in winners country of residence, FaceLift will withhold the necessary amount if the law of your country of residence demands it.
4. Jury.
4.1 Jury is a collective that selects best results for voting from the number of available for share.
4.2 Jury is formed from the founder of FaceLift Alex Pina and winners of 5 previous contests.
